tained perpendicular to it (vertical red line).<div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.332125046&amp;id=fig07">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig08a" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.332125046/asset/images/125046fig08a.jpeg" height="1004" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 8a</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.332125046&amp;id=fig08a">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig08b" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.332125046/asset/images/125046fig08b.jpeg" height="1003" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 8b</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.332125046&amp;id=fig08b">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig08c" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.332125046/asset/images/125046fig08c.jpeg" height="1187" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 8c</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a class="core-figure-download-powerpoint" href="/action/downloadFigures?doi=10.1148%2Frg.332125046&amp;id=fig08c">Download as PowerPoint</a></li></ul></div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="figure-wrap"><figure id="fig08d" class="graphic"><img src="/cms/10.1148/rg.332125046/asset/images/125046fig08d.jpeg" height="1107" width="1280" loading="lazy" /><figcaption><span class="heading">Figure 8d</span> <!-- There is no content. --><div class="core-figure-tools"><ul><li><a clas